{"tid":774262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周海媚新戲這樣耍狠…遭狠酸：零進步","createTime":"2018-08-10T07:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T11:08:59.000Z","uid":62205,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07b5185ee9960b8b7bb3be3eea0ba12beae8d7e7","tid":774262,"uid":62205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%AA%9A%E6%96%B0%E6%88%B2%E9%80%99%E6%A8%A3%E8%80%8D%E7%8B%A0-%E9%81%AD%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-%E9%9B%B6%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5-034003378.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25AA%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2580%2599%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E8%2580%258D%25E7%258B%25A0-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%258B%25A0%25E9%2585%25B8-%25E9%259B%25B6%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A5-034003378.html&d=HaxpEIr4Zh%2BcsyA%2BA%2FwXHDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f511931f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%AA%9A%E6%96%B0%E6%88%B2%E9%80%99%E6%A8%A3%E8%80%8D%E7%8B%A0-%E9%81%AD%E7%8B%A0%E9%85%B8-%E9%9B%B6%E9%80%B2%E6%AD%A5-034003378.html</a><br />\n<br />\n記者李依純／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n51歲的港星周海媚過去曾在《倚天屠龍記》中飾演周芷若，清秀扮相令觀眾難忘，還曾受封「最美周芷若」。周海媚在今年推出的新戲作品《香蜜沉沉燼如霜》中飾演天后，以資深演員姿態搭檔楊紫和鄧倫一起演出，沒想到她儘管美貌依舊，演技卻讓觀眾很不領情，開酸「這演技我也是醉了，和當年的周芷若簡直一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/154804_3c09cc40c4464557a6f56eafbe8ceaac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F154804_3c09cc40c4464557a6f56eafbe8ceaac.jpg&h=a0f0b36f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲周海媚新戲《香蜜沉沉燼如霜》劇照。（圖／翻攝自優酷微博）<br />\n<br />\n周海媚在新戲中扮演天后，因為天帝非常花心經常拈花惹草，讓她毫無安全感，人物設定偏向尖酸刻薄類型，總擔心自己的地位遭到威脅，相當沒有自信。但周海媚在演出這樣的心境時，都以「瞪大眼睛」來詮釋，讓這個「瞪眼殺」成了周海媚的招牌動作，遭到觀眾譏笑「感覺她越憤怒的時候，眼睛瞪得比雞蛋還大，完全就是表情包的操作」、「和當年的周芷若一樣，發狠只會瞪眼」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/154804_dce5e9060306bbf7215dafe28ce12f26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F154804_dce5e9060306bbf7215dafe28ce12f26.jpg&h=0b507a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼▲周海媚的招牌「瞪眼殺」遭酸演技零進步。（圖／翻攝自優酷微博）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/154804_e34940adbbfa05840edf164315ea5450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F154804_e34940adbbfa05840edf164315ea5450.jpg&h=810fa45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有大陸網友毒舌直言：「周海媚也是資深演員了，能憑藉貌美如花走紅這麼多年，如今還能在電視劇中打打醬油，畢竟很多中年女星都會遭遇這樣的尷尬，她還有戲拍已經很不錯。」只是大部分觀眾多認為，周海媚的演技沒有更多進步，表現也不夠深沉老練，反而只有「瞪眼殺」是她的特色。"},{"pid":"9f746f5dbd1c472d93b431250ceb570e86d0a43a","tid":774262,"uid":62205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C-%E7%9E%AA%E7%9C%BC%E6%AE%BA-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%AA%9A%E9%81%AD%E5%90%90%E6%A7%BD%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%AE-114442252.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%259B%25E7%2589%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E7%259E%25AA%25E7%259C%25BC%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25AA%259A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2590%2590%25E6%25A7%25BD%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25B7%25AE-114442252.html&d=HaxpEIr4Zh%2BcsyA%2BA%2FwXHDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0c86fb62\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C-%E7%9E%AA%E7%9C%BC%E6%AE%BA-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%AA%9A%E9%81%AD%E5%90%90%E6%A7%BD%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%AE-114442252.html</a><br />\n<br />\n招牌動作「瞪眼殺」 周海媚遭吐槽演技差<br />\n<br />\n51歲的港星周海媚是不少6、7年級生心目中的一代女神，她最近有新戲上檔，卻被觀眾酸溜溜地說演技根本沒有進步，為什麼呢？她在劇中不管詮釋什麼樣心境都以瞪大眼睛來表現，還有網友發現周海媚在24年前演《倚天屠龍記》時就經常用這招。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/150830_93ec0202f0b895dba329f6e24e4ddb6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F150830_93ec0202f0b895dba329f6e24e4ddb6c.jpg&h=da0e18df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖／翻攝自梨視頻微博<br />\n<br />\n曾經有著史上最美周芷若之稱，港星周海媚今年有新作品，但電視劇才播出不久，這個一代女神就晚節不保、頻頻被吐槽，不管詮釋什麼樣心境都以瞪大眼睛來表現，這個被形容是瞪眼殺的表情成了周海媚的招牌動作，大陸觀眾看不下去，還挖出24年前《倚天屠龍記》的片段，說當初周海媚就是這樣演周芷若的。<br />\n<br />\n大陸媒體：「可能是近視的原因，發覺她發怒的時候眼睛瞪得比雞蛋還大，51歲的周海媚看起來有點發福但顏值還是在線，只是這演技沒有更多進步。」<br />\n<br />\n周海媚瞪大眼睛耍狠，不知道跟她在劇中飾演反派是不是相關，但這個眼神觀眾不領情，直呼實在讓人無法直視。"},{"pid":"c67bd0bde4a16ca0e4ad6a139e86a7ac0daa8d64","tid":774262,"uid":8410,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"佢一向都唔係演技派，tvb 時代只係花瓶"},{"pid":"8fe1e23bbc076e35264397ce7427b9a125db4be4","tid":774262,"uid":91664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"睇下波算啦"},{"pid":"8f26d32d0e9309bbbb075ddae71d841227b8a5b6","tid":774262,"uid":145496,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"擺明劇本或者導演問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n當年根本無人話佢唔演得, 拍大鬧廣昌隆 不知演得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78f088cedec1536521be28ccfb019b31b6f1067","tid":774262,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"still want屌"},{"pid":"f5f452ca382b6c0648eb4d06a38171ca17056939","tid":774262,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c67bd0bde4a16ca0e4ad6a139e86a7ac0daa8d64","tid":774262,"uid":8410,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"佢一向都唔係演技派，tvb 時代只係花瓶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:40:09.000Z","msg":"小芙蓉?"},{"pid":"03a206eb5e6ab6d6c33b1f1266347a98e59d8983","tid":774262,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"年紀大左面部肌膚鬆弛左根本做唔到咁多面部表情，睇劉德華就知"},{"pid":"09583916445f97e0b6f840beb1915846c6927b7e","tid":774262,"uid":173695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03a206eb5e6ab6d6c33b1f1266347a98e59d8983","tid":774262,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"年紀大左面部肌膚鬆弛左根本做唔到咁多面部表情，睇劉德華就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撈家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e6a0c8581806fbbb7e577aa469cfd23641c51f","tid":774262,"uid":146604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:08:05.000Z","msg":"有演技一早做左視后"},{"pid":"e6d5380262db150449c55a5014d6064a63d26efb","tid":774262,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"想個表情點？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}